<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>وَمُقَابِله يضمن<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>وَمَسْجِد كطريق<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>فِي حفر بِئْر فِيهِ<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p65"></span>وَمَا تولد من جنَاح<a href="#p65" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p66"></span>بِفَتْح الْجِيم وَهُوَ البارز عَن سمت الْجِدَار<a href="#p66" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p67"></span>إِلَى شَارِع فمضمون<a href="#p67" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p68"></span>أذن فِيهِ الامام أم لَا<a href="#p68" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
